comments.body:
@Sea-n thanks for the PR.  This can't be merged now as the branch needed to be updated, and one of the CI tests failed.  I think it was a bogus test failure and I'm hoping the update I just kicked off will fix it.

FWIW, in Dark mode for me, prior to this change, the word "Build" was all in black.  I can clearly see it, at least while using Firefox, but I can understand how others might not pick it up as easily.  I do like the change that you have made, regardless, so once we get happy tests, we can move forward with this.

Thanks!

@mairin if you have a quick moment to take a peak, I'd appreciate it.
